title: Seletti - Mooca Plaza
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Healthier fast-food concept franchise offering a separated vegetarian menu section with only one item clearly marked as vegan: Rice and beans Seletti. Other dishes in this section appear to be vegan, but are not marked, so please inquire. A crepe stuffed with spinach is clearly marked on the regular menu as vegan.
